  "comment": "The Showtec Shark Wash Zoom Two is a wash moving head suitable for indoor use with seven 30-watt RGBW LEDs on board. Thanks to its motorised zoom, it can effortlessly produce a classic wash effect with a beam angle of anywhere between 6° and 38°. Dimmer and strobe functions make this moving head wash even more versatile. The Shark Wash Zoom Two can run in DMX, auto or sound modes as a master or slave, or it can be operated using the included remote control.",
